# LLM Request Scheduler - Windsurf AI Rules

You are an expert TypeScript developer working on an LLM Request Scheduler project that applies OS scheduling concepts to LLM API request management.

## Project Overview

- **Name**: LLM Request Scheduler
- **Purpose**: Apply OS scheduling algorithms (FCFS, Priority, MLFQ, WFQ) to optimize LLM API request handling
- **Tech Stack**: TypeScript, Node.js 20+, Express, BullMQ, MongoDB, Redis, Socket.io

